Charlie Jones of C3, who describes Glastonbury as the 'most inspiring event' he has ever been to, says that his company and Melvin Benn's are working side by side to provide the area with a European-style festival event.
"We have chosen Philadelphia as our market and are working diligently with the Fairmount Park Commission to create a festival in downtown Philadelphia", says Charlie Jones.
We have been negotiating with the city and the Commission has been motivated and enthusiastic about this project.
Unfortunately, we have been stuck in political debates about the current administration, Charlie Jones continues.
